title: alpha_(white93)
body:
A pixiv user who has sent request messages to a huge number of artists (using the exact same words each time), saying "please draw [[sia_(bhl930224)|my original character]]", on pixiv and other SNS boards.

He randomly changes the name and location of his profile line on a frequent basis, and makes requests for pictures of various situations (including NSFW pictures such as [[pregnancy]], [[bestiality]], [[futanari]] or [[furry]]), and then he posts the pictures on his own account/blog without giving credit to the original artists.

Part of his names: アルファ (Alpha), "LAL", 초코 (Choco), "Gin", "adirisia", "Rdi", "Rei D sia"

h4.See also

* Blog: http://blog.naver.com/bhl930224
* One of his pixiv account: http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=8388098

title: info-chan
body: Only known as "Info-chan", she is a character from the sandbox game [[Yandere Simulator]]. She provides [[ayano aishi|Yandere-chan]] with information about fellow students.

title: kokona_haruka_(yandere_simulator)
body:
Kokona Haruka is a character from the sandbox game [[Yandere Simulator]]. Recognized for her [[large breasts]] and [[purple hair|purple]] [[twin drills]], she is considered a rival of [[ayano aishi|Yandere-chan]] due her crush on [[Senpai_(yandere_simulator)|Senpai]].

Despite this characters appearance being similar to the popular [[UTAU]], [[Kasane Teto]], this was unintentional as the original base model of the character was simply a [[mikumikudance|3D model]] of Teto.

title: oka_ruto_(yandere_simulator)
body: Oka Ruto is a character from the sandbox game [[Yandere Simulator]]. She is the leader of the Occult Club and is considered a rival of [[ayano aishi|Yandere-chan]] due to her crush on [[Senpai_(yandere_simulator)|Senpai]]. She has dark [[blue hair]] and [[purple eyes]], and her accessories are a [[choker]] and [[arm warmers]].
